/p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\">这里是喜马拉雅山脉腹地</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\">冰峰连绵、空气稀薄</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">即便是在气候这么恶劣的地方</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">也有边防战士为我们放哨站岗</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\"><img class=\"\" data-copyright=\"0\" data-ratio=\"0.4934210526315789\" data-s=\"300,640\" src=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/e8b36f204c48a7ee8414b6d3957ead2a.png\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"760\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">“一年三百六十日，多是横戈马上行。”</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\">2月4日，农历除夕</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\">而在新疆军区某边防团</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\">这一天却一如往常</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\">在海拔5400多米的点位</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\">边防战士们坚守岗位</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">他们放弃与家人的团圆</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">却换来边境一线的安全</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><img class=\"\" data-copyright=\"0\" data-ratio=\"0.675\" data-s=\"300,640\" src=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/36b41d9eb5031b59f2ad86547cf1b33d.png\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\">在父母眼中</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\">他们还是个孩子</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\">但他们把青春献给了家国和边关</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">但他们深知<br style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">脚下站立的地方</span></strong><strong style=\"font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">是祖国</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong>身上肩负的是安宁</strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><img class=\"\" data-copyright=\"0\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" src=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/db2efcf717b830e56cc8b5448a3c5acb.png\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"text-align: center;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">长治久安</span></strong><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\">不是一句空洞的口号</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\">更关乎你我的</p><p style=\"white-sp