3f8cc641e5146afff741dbabdfe62.png\" style=\"color: rgb(95, 156, 239);line-height: 25.6px;\"  /></p>\n                </div>',1551943515,'','',0),(9,'空姐一声吼：“跑！”','<div class=\"rich_media_content \" id=\"js_content\">\n                    \n\n                    \n\n                    \n                    \n                    <p>3月5日凌晨，一架国航客机在执行从北京到洛杉矶的航线时，货舱出现火警，飞机在俄罗斯阿纳德尔机场备降，并实施紧急撤离程序。这一事件在微博上迅速成为热点，最触动大家的是现场视频里空姐危急时刻的一声吼：<span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong>“跑！别拿东西，跑！”</strong></span></p><p><br  /></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><img class=\"\" data-backh=\"413\" data-backw=\"556\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/66baf4eeb8a04f3c4fc96cd20eba76bb.png\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/qkQTRn2Z9NwJ5PS3QDImgEqjqZfzJw0RYva4tyUWswKjJtWF68Zx88Rd7vmp1z7ENtIfuoSYBiampGibiabtweKzw/?wx_fmt=png\" data-cropx1=\"99.93920972644378\" data-cropx2=\"450.83687943262413\" data-cropy1=\"0\" data-cropy2=\"261.5075987841945\" data-oversubscription-url=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Ow1RI6Hpia3pARUDg7LkR1nddDibBeS1CZDOIX4ClUibiaTFqIfgk11iaNm47a6bWKORpvZNEPkXwnOVjezDJ1Vq5Jw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.7435897435897436\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"351\" src=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/66baf4eeb8a04f3c4fc96cd20eba76bb.png\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 14px 0px;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\"  /></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">被紧急疏散的乘客</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"></span></p><p>3月5日下午，微博网友<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>@KOD高博</strong></span>&nbsp;发文描述了备降时的情况并同时上传了一段视频。</p><p><br  /></p><p><iframe class=\"video_iframe\" data-vidtype=\"1\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fshp.qpic.cn%2Fqqvideo_ori%2F0%2Fv1359elo1d0_496_280%2F0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" data-ratio=\"1.7777777777777777\" data-w=\"864\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/preview.html?width=500&amp;height=375&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=v1359elo1d0\"></iframe></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">来源：北京日报客户端都视频</span></p><p><br  /></p><p>@KOD高博 说，当时飞机上空乘和空姐让大家不要拿东西要赶紧撤离，而且他们是最后一批离开飞机的。根据视频，当时乘客们乘滑梯撤离，可以明显听到空姐声嘶力竭大声喊话催促着让乘客们快跑：“<span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong>跑！别拿东西，跑！”</strong></span></p><p><br  /></p><p><img class=\"\" data-backh=\"617\" data-backw=\"539\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/4a5f6503d31d5ca0462b3578f63aa3b8.png\" data-ratio=\"1.1444444444444444\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/4a5f6503d31d5ca0462b3578f63aa3b8.png\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 14px 0px;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\"  /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">@KOD高博&nbsp;微博截图</span></p><p><br  /></p><p>据网友<strong>@KOD高博</strong>&nbsp;的描述，在匆忙的撤离中，空姐把拿的毯子给了乘客，空乘把自己的鞋给了乘客，爸爸让孩子和妈妈先上车，空姐空乘让所有乘客上车他们最后上车，<span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong>“这就是人性善良的一面，看到了每个人对‘责任’这两个字的诠释。”</strong></span></p><p><br  /></p><p><img class=\" __bg_gif\" data-backh=\"556\" data-backw=\"556\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/cba85a0aebbe4042c16cd867ddc541e2.png\" data-copyright=\"0\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"480\" src=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/cba85a0aebbe4042c16cd867ddc541e2.png\" style=\"white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\"  /></p><p><br  /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">一段视频记录了冰天雪地中</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">乘客在停机坪上行走<br style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">↓↓↓</p><p><iframe class=\"video_iframe\" data-vidtype=\"1\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fshp.qpic.cn%2Fqqvideo_ori%2F0%2Fh0845beaw0v_496_280%2F0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" data-ratio=\"1.7777777777777777\" data-w=\"864\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/preview.html?width=500&amp;height=375&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=h0845beaw0v\"></iframe></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">来源：北京日报客户端都视频</span></p><p><br style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /></p><p><img class=\"\" data-backh=\"593\" data-backw=\"556\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Ow1RI6Hpia3pARUDg7LkR1nddDibBeS1CZDj6QCzmaMhzhRvwbhZcojIeVcHBdyfNQjUjo8UjyIHO1vP5Nt52soA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Ow1RI6Hpia3pARUDg7LkR1nddDibBeS1CZSiblLs4yLzJd3rnjhyLaUJopf3Nic0mrkNVQ9rbWUlM14wEc3gnibdicAg/?wx_fmt=png\" data-cropx1=\"2.693877551020408\" data-cropx2=\"286\" data-cropy1=\"132.00000000000003\" data-cropy2=\"434.1632653061225\" data-oversubscription-url=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/O9F3NTo58yp38m51xqSic5MuHVC1YmWtmic5F7GiarjeCKdXfYiao4WSwtKd31rU2dXlzSb1n57sTArVyLBRyQGbsg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.0669014084507042\" data-s=\"300,640\" src=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/730eb994aae1dc97fceb7516a025d7d2.png\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"284\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 14px 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto;\"  /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">国航空姐冰雪中抱团取暖</span></p><p><br  /></p><p>目前，人机安全。后经检查，初步判断为飞机火警信息故障。3月5日早晨，<strong>@中国国际航空</strong> 发布微博，对这一事件进行解释。</p><p><br  /></p><p><img class=\"\" data-copyright=\"0\" data-ratio=\"0.3902439024390244\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1148\" src=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/9568a97b50eebd4469099d183787b817.png\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: justify;box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 14px 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"556\" data-backh=\"217\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/9568a97b50eebd4469099d183787b817.png\"  /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /></p><p><br style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /></p><p><strong>微博通报称：</strong></p><p><br  /></p><blockquote><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">3月4日国航CA983航班（北京-洛杉矶，波音777-300ER执飞），北京时间21：13从北京首都国际机场起飞。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><br  /></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">在俄罗斯空域飞行过程中，飞机出现后货舱火警信息，机组按照火警处置程序及时进行处置。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><br  /></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">为确保安全，该航班于北京时间3月5日2：55就近安全备降俄罗斯阿纳德尔机场，并实施紧急撤离程序。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><br  /></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">通报称，事发后人机安全，全体旅客被安排在候机楼内休息。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><br  /></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">落地后经检查，飞机货舱正常且无过火痕迹，初步判断为飞机火警信息故障</span><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><br  /></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">国航已调配飞机前往俄罗斯阿纳德尔机场做好旅客后续运输工作。</span></p></blockquote><p><br  /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">国航空姐的这一声吼</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">也引发了网友的狂赞</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">网友表示：</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong>看哭了，为你们骄傲和自豪</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">↓↓↓</p><section label=\"Copyright © 2014 playhudong All Rights Reserved.\" donone=\"shifuMouseDownCard(&#39;shifu_c_021&#39;)\"><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.27294685990338163\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1242\" src=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/88a368f682a58ee26825516067327362.png\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"556\" data-backh=\"152\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/88a368f682a58ee26825516067327362.png\"  /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /></section><section label=\"Copyright © 2014 playhudong All Rights Reserved.\" donone=\"shifuMouseDownCard(&#39;shifu_c_021&#39;)\"><img class=\"\" data-backh=\"104\" data-backw=\"556\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/qkQTRn2Z9NwJ5PS3QDImgEqjqZfzJw0RgV3Jx3eK7LaLXjrmWeWbOZgLNibG6nFctbAhMfPhgu6qOWjkR8ibwVTQ/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-oversubscription-url=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/O9F3NTo58yp38m51xqSic5MuHVC1YmWtmYL0xtIIY6O2LaWttyTmDMad75xsFAZ43zdiaPGX80yibMBsMFbsialy9g/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.18679549114331723\" data-s=\"300,640\" src=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/4527f4b315fd736ff21cd4f9a0d1e486.png\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1242\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\"  /><br  /></section><s