\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br  /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br  /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">这位紫色头发的自由女神，保安叔叔都看不下去要驱赶了<img class=\"W_img_face\" data-ratio=\"1\" src=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/8bd63c77dc3eb86ac39180f3700a36d4.png\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"36\" style=\"border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 18px;height: 18px;vertical-align: -4px;font-family: Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;text-align: start;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" title=\"[允悲]\" type=\"face\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"text-align: right;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: 1px;\">（内容</span><span style=\"text-align: right;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: 1px;\">来源于网络，侵删）</span></p>\n                </div>',1552019860,'','',0),(31,'这些寻宠启示真的不是开玩笑的吗？感觉找到的几率十分渺茫啊','<div class=\"rich_media_content \" id=\"js_content\">\n                    \n\n                    \n\n                    \n                    \n                    <p style=\"margin-top: 1em;border: 0px;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: 18px;line-height: 27px;font-family: helvetica, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(93, 93, 93);text-align: start;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">相信很多网友都遇到过自己爱宠丢失的问题，这时心急如焚的你一定会满世界的找它们了吧？可寻宠启示要怎么写才能彰显特色并且让路人们留意呢？是显示“长宽高”，“体积面积”作为启示内容呢，还是要亲自动手来描述个人爱宠的特点呢？可以说是五花八门，只有你想不到，没有你见不到。那下面咱就来看看以下丢失爱宠主人们的精彩发布吧。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em;border: 0px;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: 18px;line-height: 27px;font-family: helvetica, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(93, 93, 93);text-align: start;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“给你一张漫画自己体会”这可能是一张别出心裁的寻狗启示了吧。连狗子“离家出走”时穿的衣服都还历历在目，就不能平时多给狗子拍几张照片嘛？人要美，狗子也是有同等权利的，总是好过这突如其来的惊吓吧。真心希望这位主子能够有合理的照片，即便是配图，也找个相对专业人士来作画一幅，就算是为了达到目击者们的精准判断力，也绝不含糊。话不多说，可能很多人都已笑晕在厕所了。</p><p><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.059375\" src=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/ecd57345abaaa17d4e7404f2bdadaca8.png\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"margin: 1em auto;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-family: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;display: block;border-radius: 4px;\"></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-family: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;\"><br  /></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em;border: 0px;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: 18px;line-height: 27px;font-family: helvetica, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(93, 93, 93);text-align: start;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">猫咪可能是最容易走失并且难抓到的动物了吧？矫捷的行动，不凡的身手，真的可谓世外高猫了。一般陌生人确实是很难降服的。尽管寻找历程如此艰难，还是希望主人的寻猫启示能再多些描述，好让喵主能早日归来，同样也是为了更多的目击者辨识以好联络。要不然只能是眼睁睁的看着一只神奇的动物从眼前一闪而过了。</p><p><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3451612903225807\" src=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/98fdbad1e5c2371720832404815ba115.png\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"620\" style=\"margin: 1em auto;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-family: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;display: block;border-radius: 4px;\"></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-family: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;\"><br  /></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em;border: 0px;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: 18px;line-height: 27px;font-family: helvetica, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(93, 93, 93);text-align: start;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这……相信这不是同一只狗子吧，原谅我发出了猪一般的笑声。看来这狗子是出去串了个门回来了，依旧呆在平时常在的地方，淡定自若的等主人发放零食吧。要不然主人耗费了人力物力财力才做好的寻狗启示这不是白弄了么。还是说主人对你的智商多有不信任，总觉得你出去串门了就很难找到回家的路~不管怎么说，回来了就是好事，好事啊！</p><p><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3454545454545455\" src=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/59e2a08eb71f0c5fca297f016b600a51.png\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"440\" style=\"margin: 1em auto;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-family: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;display: block;border-radius: 4px;\"></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-family: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;\"><br  /></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em;border: 0px;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: 18px;line-height: 27px;font-family: helvetica, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(93, 93, 93);text-align: start;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原谅这位主人放飞自我的介绍丢失的爱宠，其实狗子的颜值和寻回奖金不重要，能找到才是最重要的。我们可以忽略微乎其微的奖励，还是会多留心并帮助主人寻找的，只是希望这位主人不要这么逗好不好，本来是件很严肃的事，结果让众人不经意间都笑了场……</p><p><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" src=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/95e34dba3d478d47026536f1a69c552f.png\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"margin: 1em auto;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-family: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;display: block;border-radius: 4px;\"></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-family: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;\"><br  /></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em;border: 0px;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: 18px;line-height: 27px;font-family: helvetica, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(93, 93, 93);text-align: start;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">言简意赅的“漫画插图”，配上必有的联系方式。这确实是一份合格的寻找启示，只是总觉得少了点什么，是不是绘画手法太过无厘头了，让大伙的眼神为之一振。</p><p><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.423529411764706\" src=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/09e2a511b54ae630e06646652b91788b.png\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"425\" style=\"margin: 1em auto;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-family: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;display: block;border-radius: 4px;\"></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-family: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;\"><br  /></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em;border: 0px;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: 18px;line-height: 27px;font-family: helvetica, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(93, 93, 93);text-align: start;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">人间自有真情在，还是有很多好心人碰到了路上走丢的可怜虫，然后带回家蹭吃蹭喝的情况。可能这位主人原本还是最喜欢自家猫的，结果收留了这货以后可能是“磁场不对”，决心帮忙寻找心急如焚的愿主人了吧。希望此汪早日回归自己的家庭。“回头是岸”呐~</p><p><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2703125\" src=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/ccd33e3ad9edf0f194dbd1249a0bc814.png\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"margin: 1em auto;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-family: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;display: block;border-radius: 4px;\"></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-family: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;\"><br  /></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em;border: 0px;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: 18px;line-height: 27px;font-family: helvetica, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(93, 93, 93);text-align: start;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">感觉这主人是受尽了委屈的说，为哈说的这么渗人呢。相信当时拍这张照片的时候没有受伤，也不是在本狗丢失前拍的最后一张。同样也是希望善始善终，有人捡到了最好是物归原主，毕竟大家都觉得狗子和你在一起才是最快乐的，话说：狗随谁来着？</p><p><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3681818181818182\" src=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/35a82c9a197da8cd5e5bbe51655a5f55.png\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"440\" style=\"margin: 1em auto;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-family: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;display: block;border-radius: 4px;\"></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-family: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;\"><br  /></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em;border: 0px;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: 18px;line-height: 27px;font-family: helvetica, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(93, 93, 93);text-align: start;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">自古只有养了二哈，人生才算是“完整”吧。让你体验和其他狗与众不同的生活体验。经常跑丢的二哈确实是很多，但是不物归原主的却很少。毕竟一边投入，一边又张贴丢失信息的心情谁都不想体会。</p><p><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4407407407407407\" src=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/abbec13f3ba820f9c191a6c22017a698.png\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"540\" style=\"margin: 1em auto;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-family: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;display: block;border-radius: 4px;\"></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-family: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;\"><br  /></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em;border: 0px;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: 18px;line-height: 27px;font-family: helvetica, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(93, 93, 93);text-align: start;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一只伤病在身的狗子还能被主人用心以待，还是很幸福的，只是希望主人能附上电话，说不定有特别喜欢的还能通过电话了解狗子更多的信息，让你的狗子一夜间变成小区“宇宙无敌棒小宠”呢。</p><p><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3041237113402062\" src=\"http://pnh74b4av.bkt.clouddn.com/4e193b14e8a43101f302346f8b27a68b.png\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"582\" style=\"margin: 1em auto;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-family: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;word-break: break-word;display: block;border-radius: 4px;\"></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;lin